  "detailed_description": "Surpass your limits and ascend to the peak to meet Vinterget, the god of winter. Hurry, your daughter needs you!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use your axe as a grappling tool to skillfully swing across the levels. Build momentum and launch yourself to great distances.<br></li><li> Fight enemies that block your way.<br></li><li> Use timing and precision to get through various platforming challenges. <br></li><li> Moving platforms, disappearing platforms, icy slopes, pitfalls, moving spikes and more.<br></li><li> Beat the game in your own time in short levels that automatically save your progress, or speedrun to the finish line.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328410/extras/5e769105590e0c0760111a108fb7ed41.poster.avif?t=1695142685\" width=628 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328410/extras/5e769105590e0c0760111a108fb7ed41.webm?t=1695142685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328410/extras/5e769105590e0c0760111a108fb7ed41.mp4?t=1695142685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Surpass your limits and ascend to the peak to meet Vinterget, the god of winter. Hurry, your daughter needs you!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use your axe as a grappling tool to skillfully swing across the levels. Build momentum and launch yourself to great distances.<br></li><li> Fight enemies that block your way.<br></li><li> Use timing and precision to get through various platforming challenges. <br></li><li> Moving platforms, disappearing platforms, icy slopes, pitfalls, moving spikes and more.<br></li><li> Beat the game in your own time in short levels that automatically save your progress, or speedrun to the finish line.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328410/extras/5e769105590e0c0760111a108fb7ed41.poster.avif?t=1695142685\" width=628 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328410/extras/5e769105590e0c0760111a108fb7ed41.webm?t=1695142685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328410/extras/5e769105590e0c0760111a108fb7ed41.mp4?t=1695142685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
